==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gradualness
<hw>Grad"u*al*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of
being gradual; regular progression or gradation; slowness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>gradualness</qex> of this movement.</q> <rj><qau>M.
Arnold.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>gradualness</qex> of growth is a characteristic which
strikes the simplest observer.</q> <rj><qau>H. Drummond.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Graduate</ent>⟦br⟧
